            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-05/001_2.jpg?VersionId=4tv.qtUyNHECJz9tlw.08d7qZPjDu8ki&amp;itok=4fJ0OExb" title="北京副市长、公安局局长亓延军，已兼任中国公安部副部长。（互联网）" alt="北京副市长、公安局局长亓延军，已兼任中国公安部副部长。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-05/001_2.jpg?VersionId=4tv.qtUyNHECJz9tlw.08d7qZPjDu8ki&amp;itok=4fJ0OExb" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
